live each day as if it was your last, someday you'll most 
certainly be right.' It made an impression on me, and since then,
for the past 33 years, I have looked in the mirror every morning and asked myself: 'If today were the last day of my life, would I 
want to do what I am about to do today?' And whenever the answer 
has been 'no' for too many days in a row, I know I need to change something."

--Steve Jobs
